{"tid":1766551,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，係時候還KOLOR一個名分","createTime":"2019-12-02T16:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T05:51:30.000Z","uid":48771,"like":172,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"806ffa4a8c35758fe6f909fb6e89efd3c7bcc2e9","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"有關KOLOR嘅歌有幾黃，有幾值得欣賞，可以直接睇呢個post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758189</a><br />\n<br />\n由佢地出道到獨立到而家，佢地為音樂付出好多，一首又一首作品，有隊員甚至朝早返正職，夜晚繼續音樂都堅持落去；為香港，佢地由寫歌（天地會一定要識！），去到演唱會design，再去到遊行爭取普選，直到今時今日發夢，你都可以見到佢地嘅身影。<br />\n<br />\n只係因為佢地係獨立樂隊，好少機會而令佢地無人問津，難得今年大家有機會，我希望大家可以認識佢地多少少，投下你地嘅一票，支持一隊默默為香港付出嘅樂隊。<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係話Rubberband唔夠好，但佢地真係同903 friend底好多機會，真係好希望大家今年可以畀返個機會畀KOLOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17ee8491d8e4b3393565f3cf29711dc820f7f7e","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8233a80a71322d99c164070490ca0e9c61ed64bf","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c21a8ec8845dd10249d8695de7efaeb1301b8dc","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa326e172f53dcfb9fb8e107b81902bf1da7eea4","tid":1766551,"uid":305710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d503b2e324ea675133c58e6b7f022168e95f38","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"185c092d49b7f304338f3b699066ea734a86daaa","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"928f23a2c73109f6a10bf8035c3f103fe7c8aace","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a445b04c74e5e0dcec9c6cc632f8a1d65374f3e","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b019860b770be5f9c5097e340746225c07366ab2","tid":1766551,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"好似大局已定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa470f14d8e0fde1afd044afea8a14cc7f68ba9","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wgHnMtfo_YY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwgHnMtfo_YY&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=a9748912\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wgHnMtfo_YY</a><br />\n<br />\n送畀咁多位香港人，天地會！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 我們學說謊  我們馴服在演講<br />\r\n 似螻蟻沒發生碰撞<br />\r\n 人工的烏托邦   藏溫室不會受創<br />\r\n 貨輪似同化般泊岸<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 搖滾中醒覺   那信仰  埋藏在雪地<br />\r\n 那一天   吃掉亦記起<br />\r\n 若果哭聲  原來為獻媚<br />\r\n 像金色太陽  哪會再起<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 埋葬昨天理想  投身今天戰場<br />\r\n 錯愛錢幣肖像<br />\r\n 城市快將要死   如果這都算正常<br />\r\n 你我結這壞賬<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 老年若記起   少年時曾踏禁地<br />\r\n 揭露各權貴的禁忌<br />\r\n 成長於這世紀<br />\r\n 隨波中一再斷臂<br />\r\n 禁欲禁言禁天禁地<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 如基因複製   安於軌  完全沒破例<br />\r\n 令偏鋒判罪犯了規<br />\r\n 人生高低全聯繫貨幣<br />\r\n 讓獅子遜位  佔領母體<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 埋葬昨天理想  投身今天戰場<br />\r\n 錯愛錢幣肖像<br />\r\n 城市快將要死   如果這都算正常<br />\r\n 你我結這壞賬<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 未麻木的  終於會脫離<br />\r\n 制度壓迫  一朝過期<br />\r\n 復明現光  青天破八旗<br />\r\n 欲蓋是獸皮   人性是契機<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 埋葬昨天理想  投身今天戰場<br />\r\n 錯愛錢幣肖像<br />\r\n 城市快將要死   如果這都算正常<br />\r\n 你我結這壞賬<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 還我昨天理想  離隊抽身戰場<br />\r\n 和諧原是這樣<br />\r\n 城市永不會死   搖滾終於會破牆<br />\r\n 世界有天合唱"},{"pid":"46d8a1d5748efeba4cd80c0f457af1a349f9bd56","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b019860b770be5f9c5097e340746225c07366ab2","tid":1766551,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"好似大局已定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"盡做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49002962b5a34534d646db74fdaf660d22fc53c4","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74c2c7e3d0746e9b1f37522c82388209e7e1bac3","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"求大家幫幫手叫身邊未投嘅all in KOLOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5ff30abd40d56a8576f65e0a91d0393e5d6049","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"070cd943502677241493dad0a8c8754f00e9f61a","tid":1766551,"uid":48771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8f5a687f4151560561e2494985e70985def1e02","tid":1766551,"uid":96708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"當願榮光歸香港都想推到903有獎你就知indie band係無人會理，幾黃都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb78e88b418e77b5dc82219287dd4d546b868221","tid":1766551,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f74c62497d84046b4c6120